title: Blackfield discography 2004-2013 (FLAC)
description:
Blackfield discography 2004-2013 in FLAC quality.

Including:

Studio Albums

2004 - Blackfield (+bonus tracks)
2007 - Blackfield II
2011 - Welcome to My DNA
2013 - Blackfield IV

The first album, Blackfield, includes three additional bonus tracks issued on a later pressing that contained the original album track listing and the three bonus track on the same CD:

1. "Perfect World" (3:52)
2. "Where Is My Love?"  (3:01)
3. "Cloudy Now (Live)" (3:43)
